{"tid":1534362,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［故事］我屋企中立家姐嘅Facebook Post","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:32:52.000Z","uid":273923,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2fbde7cac862d240b1399860834ded650ef08c","tid":1534362,"uid":273923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"發佈時間：9月1日 01:25<br />\n<br />\n今日又返夜，其實我真係好唔中意返星期六深水埗鋪夜更，啲客騎呢都算啦，近排次次星期六就成班黑衣人塞住旺角，次次地鐵站一出就超嘈。半夜大叫搞到我想瞓都瞓唔著。間劏房仲要勁應聲，頂你。今日去到太子站直頭嘈到帶住耳筒都聽到啲人叫，已經超眼瞓仲要比人嘈住，我決定合埋眼開大音樂繼續休息！返到間所謂屋企已經眼瞓到死，即灘上床！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n發佈時間：9月2日 00:57<br />\n<br />\n今日終於可以靜下，班黑衣人入哂機場，條街當堂靜哂！收工坐地鐵勁少人，難得有位坐仲可以襟下電話，今日全日都唔得閒睇電話，勁多miss call 同message、個個問我去左邊。唔知點解覺得好煩，所以全部已讀不回，咩都唔想理。到太子站好自然咁落左車想行兩步返屋企，成個站一個人都無，唔止黑衣人，直頭一個人都無，好舒服好靜。返到去又即刻灘上床，今日好靜好好瞓。"},{"pid":"f04a9473492b2cba38edf625144a81a8907c4ee0","tid":1534362,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7fb8f03e9c2cbe7cecf83b3a9aaba2edcda64bd","tid":1534362,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"幫手打柒自己家姐"},{"pid":"c7010444286648474fa60435ed774e952a11d31b","tid":1534362,"uid":285855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=cbbb9259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=669b1939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=05b8f4e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png</a>"},{"pid":"23ae77a240b0c74ee3259ca7566411cd7d323c09","tid":1534362,"uid":261914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"無link？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d85db8f281023a416f0f7442b631da5136cda1","tid":1534362,"uid":310030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:40:06.000Z","msg":"你肯定係中立?"},{"pid":"d62e35f9f1b2d2c484b4780bec9a1fb4372fb313","tid":1534362,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"好似以前腥架啲廢文日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57913e8f2437c32947d384751eb7d25c460ec37","tid":1534362,"uid":232854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"港豬日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125bc94d41f6dfce7d624bae83e22b71dbf82ed3","tid":1534362,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金  全民提款日</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"abaa061020b86a2a3516070cde9f1ca34d465bfc","tid":1534362,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼 8條命 1117被捕 無數斷手斷腳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831黨鐵恐襲傷者消息全無</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n九二九三大三罷！<br />\n設死線 升級持續罷工<br />\n日日罷工 日日入機場<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span>